{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"dur","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/dur","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p>该属性标识了动画的简单持续时间。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>动画定时属性</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#clock-value\" title=\"en/SVG/Content_type#Clock-value\">&lt;clock-value&gt;</a> | <strong>indefinite</strong></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>No</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/animate.html#DurAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"clock-value\"><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#clock-value\" title=\"en/SVG/Content type#Clock-value\">&lt;clock-value&gt;</a></dt>\n <dd>指定简单持续时间的时长。值必须大于 0。可以用小时（h）、分钟（m）、秒（s）、毫秒（ms）表达这个值。可以组合这些时间表达式以提供一个复合的持续时间，比如这样：<code>hh:mm:ss.iii</code>或者这样：<code>mm:ss.iii</code>。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>如果一个动画元素不带有<code>dur</code>属性，简单持续时间就是无限期的。请注意：如果一个简单持续时间是无限期的，则插值不能起作用（虽然它对&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/set\"><code>&lt;set&gt;</code></a> 元素依然是有用的）。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用<code>dur</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#animation\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Animation\">动画元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"dur","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"dur","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/dur","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/dur/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/dur","title":"dur"}],"pageTitle":"dur - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}